let schema=datatable(OccurrenceTime:datetime,EventType:string,count_:long)[];
let HypervEvents = datatable(C_EventID:string,Category:string,EventDescription:string, InterruptionFlag:bool)
        [
            "13002",    "vmCreated",                        "VM created successfully",                                                  false,
            "13003",    "vmDeleted",                        "VM deleted successfully",                                                  false,
            "18504",    "vmShutdownByForce",                "VM shutdown by force",                                                     true,
            "18508",    "vmShudownByGuestOS",               "VM was shut down by the guest operating system",                           false,
            "18590",    "vmCrashed",                        "Hyper-V Critical error in OS",                                             true,
            "18514",    "vmResetByGuestOS",                 "VM was reset by Guest OS",                                                 false,
            "18560",    "vmTripleFault",                    "MSVM_TRIPLE_FAULT_UNRECOVERABLE_EXCEPTION_EVENT_ID",                       true,
            "12030",    "vmStartFailure",                   "HYPERV_START_FAILURE_EVENT_ID",                                            true,
            "12630",    "vmResiliencyFailure",               "HYPERV VM Resiliency Failure",                                            true,
            "18512",    "vmCreated",                        "VM created successfully",                                                  false,
            "18516",    "vmPaused",                         "VM paused",                                                                true,
            "18518",    "vmResumed",                        "VM is resumed",                                                            false,
            "12597",    "vmConnected",                      "Connected to virtual network",                                             false,
            "12598",    "vmDisconnected",                   "Disconnected from virtual network",                                        false,
            "18500",    "vmStarted",                        "VM started successfully(Microsoft-Windows-Hyper-V-Worker)",                false,
            "12582",    "vmStartedSynthNic",                "VM started successfully(Microsoft-Windows-Hyper-V-SynthNic)",              false,
            "18601",    "vmBooted",                         "VM successfully booted an operating system",                               false,
            //below events are mainly required
            "18502",    "vmTurnedOff",                      "Hyper-V Turned off",                                                       false,
            "18510",    "vmSaved",                          "VM saved sucessfully",                                                     true,
            "18524",    "vmPausedCritical",                 "Hyper-V VM Paused for critical error",                                     true,
            "20417",    "vmLongBlackout",                   "Hyper-V Live Migration Long Blackout",                                     true,
            "12050",    "vmRestoreFailure",                 "VM Restore Failed",                                                        true,
            "5120",     "csvAutoPause",                     "CSV Auto Pause Error",                                                     true,
            "21026",    "vmLMFailureSource",                "HyperV Live Migration Failure at Source",                                  true,
            "21024",    "vmLMFailureDestination",           "HyperV Live Migration Failure at Destination",                             true,
            "24004",    "vmProcessorFeatureFailure",        "Hyper-V Processor-specific features not supported",                        true,
        ];
let HyperVEventDescriptionTable = datatable(EventId:int,Category:string,EventType:string)
[
//    18502,"vmTurnedOff","Hyper-V VM Turned off",
    18590,"vmCrashed","Hyper-V Critical error in OS",
    18510,"vmSaved","Hyper-V VM Saved",
    18560,"vmTripleFault","MSVM_TRIPLE_FAULT_UNRECOVERABLE_EXCEPTION_EVENT_ID",
    12030,"vmStartFailure", "HYPERV_START_FAILURE_EVENT_ID",
    18516,"vmPaused","Hyper-V VM Paused",
    20417,"vmLongBlackout","Hyper-V Live Migration Long Blackout",
    18524,"vmPausedCritical","Hyper-V VM Paused for critical error",
    12630,"vmResiliencyFailure","Hyper-V VM Resiliency Failure",
    12050,"vmRestoreFailure","VM Restore Failed",
    5120,"csvAutoPause","CSV Auto Pause Error",
    21026,"vmLMFailureSource","HyperV Live Migration Failure at Source",
    21024,"vmLMFailureDestination","HyperV Live Migration Failure at Destination",
    24004,"vmProcessorFeatureFailure","Hyper-V Processor-specific features not supported"
];
let InterruptionList = HyperVEventDescriptionTable | summarize makeset(EventId);
let InterestingEvents = HypervEvents | summarize makeset(C_EventID);
let data=(
    database('db').['WindowsEventLogs']
    | apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime
    | where LogName startswith "Microsoft-Windows-Hyper-V" and EventId in (InterestingEvents)
    | extend VmName = tostring(Properties[0]), VmId = tostring(Properties[1])
    | distinct VmName,VmId,OccurrenceTime,MachineName,EventId,RecordId,Description
    | sort by VmName, VmId, OccurrenceTime asc 
    | extend Interruption = iif((VmName != next(VmName,1) or VmId != next(VmId,1) or next(EventId,1) == "13003") and EventId in (InterruptionList),
                                iif(EventId in ("18502","18504"), 0, 1),
                                iif(EventId in (InterruptionList),1,0)
                            )
    | where Interruption == 1
    | join kind=inner HyperVEventDescriptionTable on EventId 
    //| extend VmName = tostring(Properties[0]), VmId = tostring(Properties[1])
    | distinct OccurrenceTime,MachineName,EventId,RecordId,Description,Category,EventType,VmName 
    | extend VmType = iff(strlen(VmName) >= 36, "Tenant", "Infra")
    | where VmType == "Tenant"
);
union isfuzzy=true schema,data
| apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime

union isfuzzy=true view,(
    union withsource=source cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<None>')
    .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.ActionPlan*']
    | extend Database=extract("database\\(\\\"([\\w-.]*)\\\"\\)",1,source)
    | distinct MachineName,EventName,OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName,ActionPlanStatus,ActivityID,Database
    | extend ActionPlanInstanceId=tostring(ActionPlanInstanceId),MachineName=tostring(MachineName)
    | summarize (StartTime,StartEventName)=arg_min(OccurrenceTime,EventName),(StopTime,ActionPlanStatus,StopEventName)=arg_max(OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanStatus,EventName),ActionPlanName=any(ActionPlanName),MachineName=any(MachineName) by ActionPlanInstanceId,Database
    | where StartEventName=="ActionPlan/Start" or StopEventName=="ActionPlan/Stop" // Cleaning the data of entries without a start or stop event
    | where ActionPlanName != "TestControlPlane"
    | project ActionPlanStatus,ActionPlan=strcat(ActionPlanName," (",ActionPlanInstanceId,")"),Duration=StopTime-StartTime,StartTime,StopTime,ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName,Database,MachineName
    | extend Cluster='apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>'
    | order by ActionPlanStatus asc

    union withsource=source database('db')
    .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.ActionPlan*']
    | distinct MachineName,EventName,OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName,ActionPlanStatus,ActivityID
    | extend ActionPlanInstanceId=tostring(ActionPlanInstanceId),MachineName=tostring(MachineName)

    | extend ActionPlanSuccess=toint(ActionPlanStatus=="Success"), ActionPlanFailed=toint(ActionPlanStatus=="Error")
    | extend Total = ActionPlanSuccess + ActionPlanFailed
)

{"cluster":"help.kusto.windows.net","database":"Samples","query":"alias database db =cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<None>');
let view=datatable(ActionPlanStatus:string,ActionPlan:string,Duration:timespan,StartTime:datetime,StopTime:datetime,ActionPlanInstanceId:string,ActionPlanName:string,ActionPlanSuccess:int,ActionPlanFailed:int)[];
union isfuzzy=true view,(
    union withsource=source database('db')
    .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.ActionPlan*']
    | distinct MachineName,EventName,OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName,ActionPlanStatus,ActivityID
    | extend ActionPlanInstanceId=tostring(ActionPlanInstanceId),MachineName=tostring(MachineName)
    | summarize (StartTime,StartEventName)=arg_min(OccurrenceTime,EventName),(StopTime,ActionPlanStatus,StopEventName)=arg_max(OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanStatus,EventName),ActionPlanName=any(ActionPlanName),MachineName=any(MachineName) by ActionPlanInstanceId
    | where StartEventName=="ActionPlan/Start" or StopEventName=="ActionPlan/Stop" // Cleaning the data of entries without a start or stop event
    | where ActionPlanName != "TestControlPlane"
    | project ActionPlanStatus,ActionPlan=strcat(ActionPlanName," (",ActionPlanInstanceId,")"),Duration=StopTime-StartTime,StartTime,StopTime,ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName,MachineName
    | extend ActionPlanSuccess=toint(ActionPlanStatus=="Success"), ActionPlanFailed=toint(ActionPlanStatus=="Error")

let startTime = toscalar(union database("db").['ETL-Microsoft-VaaS*'] | apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime | summarize min(OccurrenceTime));
let endTime = toscalar(union database("db").['ETL-Microsoft-VaaS*'] | apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime | summarize max(OccurrenceTime));
let binval = 10m;
let zeroTimeTable =  (range x from 1 to 1 step 1
    | mvexpand OccurrenceTime = range(startTime, endTime, binval) to typeof(datetime));
database('db').['ETL-CrpServiceEventSource.ApiQosEvent']
| where OperationName=="VirtualMachines.ResourceOperation.PUT" //or OperationName=="VirtualMachines.ResourceOperation.DELETE"
| where ResultType!=1
| distinct OccurrenceTime,OperationName,ResultType,DurationInMilliseconds,ResultCode,CorrelationId
| where OccurrenceTime<endTime and OccurrenceTime>startTime
| apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime
| summarize OccurrenceTime=max(OccurrenceTime),ResultCode=strcat(makeset(ResultCode)),ResultType=any(ResultType),FirstToLastInMs=tolong((max(OccurrenceTime)-min(OccurrenceTime))/1ms) by CorrelationId
| join kind=leftouter (
    database('db').['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-Compute-Pipeline.VmPipelineRunStop']
    | distinct OccurrenceTime,CorrelationId,DurationInMs,Exception
    | summarize DurationInMs=sum(DurationInMs),Exception=any(Exception) by CorrelationId)

| union zeroTimeTable
| summarize

    Failed=countif(isValue==true and isSuccess==false),

| summarize OccurrenceTime=max(OccurrenceTime),ResultCode=strcat(makeset(ResultCode)),ResultType=any(ResultType),FirstToLastInMs=tolong((max(OccurrenceTime)-min(OccurrenceTime))/1ms) by CorrelationId
| join kind=leftouter (
    database('db').['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-Compute-Pipeline.VmPipelineRunStop']
    | distinct OccurrenceTime,CorrelationId,DurationInMs,Exception

on CorrelationId

{"cluster":"help.kusto.windows.net","database":"Samples","query":"alias database db = cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<help>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<Samples>');
let view=datatable(FileName:string,LineNumber:long,FileLineContent:string)[];
union isfuzzy=true view,database('db').['TextFileLogs']
| where FileName endswith "Get-AzureStackLog_Output.log" and FileName notcontains "archive"
| where 
    FileLineContent contains "Invoke-AzureStackLogCollection : Collecting logs from"
    or FileLineContent contains "Get-FilteredRoleName : Filtering by role"
    or FileLineContent contains "Get-RolePublicInfoFromCustomerConfig : Roles in the configuration file:"
    or FileLineContent startswith "PS>TerminatingError"
    or FileLineContent contains "Get-FolderAsZip : An error"
| where FileLineContent notcontains "(Get-EceConfiguration): "
| parse kind = regex FileLineContent with * "Invoke-AzureStackLogCollection : Collecting logs from " StartTime ' to ' EndTime 'M*' *
| parse kind = regex FileLineContent with * 'Get-FilteredRoleName : Filtering by ' RoleList 
| parse kind = regex FileLineContent with * "Get-RolePublicInfoFromCustomerConfig : Roles in the configuration file: " AllRoleList
| parse kind = regex FileLineContent with "(^)" "PS>TerminatingError" ErrorList
| parse kind = regex FileLineContent with * "Get-FolderAsZip : An error" ErrorList2
| project FileName,LineNumber,StartTime,EndTime,RoleList,AllRoleList,ErrorList=coalesce(ErrorList,ErrorList2)
| summarize StartTime=any(StartTime),EndTime=any(EndTime),RoleList=any(RoleList),AllRoleList=any(AllRoleList),ErrorDetails=strcat_array(makeset(iff(not(isempty(ErrorList)),strcat("Line ",LineNumber,": ",ErrorList),""),1000),"\r\n") by FileName
| project FileName,StartTime,EndTime,RoleList=coalesce(RoleList,AllRoleList,"None"),ErrorDetails=trim_start("\r\n",ErrorDetails)
| order by FileName desc
| extend Cluster='apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<help>', Database='apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<Samples>'

    | distinct MachineName,LogName,ProviderName,EventId,RecordId,Level,OccurrenceTime,Description,tostring(Properties)

[

let InterestingEventIDs = toscalar(InterestingEventTable | summarize makeset(EventId));
let InterestingProviders = toscalar(InterestingEventTable | summarize makeset(ProviderName));
union isfuzzy=true schema,(
    find withsource=Source in (database('db').['WindowsEventLogs'])
        where EventId in (InterestingEventIDs) and ProviderName in (InterestingProviders)
        project OccurrenceTime,MachineName,LogName,ProviderName,EventId,RecordId,Level,Description,Properties
    | apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime
    | distinct MachineName,LogName,ProviderName,EventId,RecordId,Level,OccurrenceTime,Description,tostring(Properties)
    | join kind=inner (InterestingEventTable) on ProviderName,EventId
    | project-away ProviderName1,EventId1
)

{"cluster":"help.kusto.windows.net","database":"Samples","query":"alias database db = cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<help>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<Samples>');
let maxDurationInMin = 100;
let zerotable = (range DurationInMin from 1 to maxDurationInMin step 1 | extend Succeeded=toint(0),Failed=toint(0));
union isfuzzy=true zerotable,(
    database('db').['ETL-CrpServiceEventSource.ApiQosEvent']
    | where OperationName startswith "VirtualMachines." and not(OperationName endswith "GET")
    | distinct OccurrenceTime,OperationName,ResultType,CorrelationId,E2EDurationInMilliseconds,ResourceName,ErrorDetails
    | apply_attribute lens:time:OccurrenceTime
    | extend extracted=extractall(@"(?:VirtualMachines\.)(\w*)(?:\.)(DELETE|PUT|POST)", OperationName)
    | extend Method=tostring(extracted[0][1]), OpType=tostring(extracted[0][0])
    | project-away extracted
    | join kind=leftouter (
        database('db').['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-Compute-Pipeline.VmPipelineRunStop']
        | distinct OccurrenceTime,VmName,CorrelationId,DurationInMs,Exception
        | summarize DurationInMs=sum(DurationInMs),Exception=any(Exception) by VmName,CorrelationId)
    on CorrelationId,$left.ResourceName == $right.VmName
    | where Method=="PUT"
    | extend Succeeded=toint(isempty(Exception) and isempty(ErrorDetails) and (ResultType==0 or ResultType==1))
    | extend Failed=toint(1-Succeeded)
    | extend DurationInMin=coalesce(DurationInMs/60000,E2EDurationInMilliseconds/60000,0)
    | project Succeeded,Failed,DurationInMin
)

{"cluster":"help.kusto.windows.net","database":"Samples","query":"let APlan='apply_attribute lens:value:ActionPlan?<None>';
let view=datatable(Name:string,ActionPlanName:string,StartTime:datetime, EndTime:datetime,ActionPlanInstanceId:string,ActionPlan:string)[];
union isfuzzy=true view,(
    union withsource=source cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<None>')
    .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.StepStart']
    | summarize StartTime=arg_min(OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanInstanceId) by ActionPlanInstanceId,Name,FullyQualifiedId
    | join (
            union cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<None>')
            .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.StepStop']
            | summarize EndTime=arg_max(OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanInstanceId) by ActionPlanInstanceId,FullyQualifiedId
    ) on ActionPlanInstanceId,FullyQualifiedId
    | join kind=leftouter ( 
            union cluster('apply_attribute lens:value:Cluster?<None>').database('apply_attribute lens:value:Database?<None>')
           .['ETL-Microsoft-AzureStack-CloudEngine.ActionPlan*']
           | summarize (EndTime,ActionPlanStatus)=arg_max(OccurrenceTime,ActionPlanStatus) by ActionPlanInstanceId,ActionPlanName
    ) on ActionPlanInstanceId
    | project Name=strcat(FullyQualifiedId," ",Name), ActionPlanName, StartTime , EndTime, ActionPlanInstanceId, ActionPlan=strcat(ActionPlanName," (",ActionPlanInstanceId1,")")
    | apply_attribute lens:time:StartTime
    | where ActionPlan == APlan
)
